---
const copingMechanisms = [
  {
    title: "Tighter prompts, sharper SKILL.md",
    helps: "Fewer weird runs this week.",
    plateaus:
      "The instructions are tuned to a model that gets replaced on someone else's schedule.",
  },
  {
    title: "Rerun it a few times, eyeball the output",
    helps: "Catches the obvious.",
    plateaus:
      "Doesn't scale past a handful of skills, and leaves no record anyone else can trust.",
  },
  {
    title: "A hand-rolled eval harness in CI",
    helps: "Real engineering, honest intent.",
    plateaus:
      "A side project someone owns forever — and it still doesn't know what a skill version is.",
  },
  {
    title: "An eval bench in another tab",
    helps: "Real scores.",
    plateaus:
      "Scores what you thought to ask, once, on a copy you now keep in sync.",
  },
];
---

<section id="coping" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
      the sensible things
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-3xl">
      You&#39;ve already tried the fixes.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-ink-dim leading-relaxed">
      You&#39;ve adapted — everyone shipping skills has. The adaptations
      are real, they help, and we used every one of them. Here&#39;s
      where each one plateaus.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
    {
      copingMechanisms.map((mechanism) => (
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">{mechanism.title}</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase text-ink-dim">It helps: </span>
            <span class="text-ink">{mechanism.helps}</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase text-ink-dim">Where it plateaus: </span>
            <span class="text-ink-dim">{mechanism.plateaus}</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-ink">
    They all treat the symptom — this output, this run, this scare. The
    cause is one level down.
  </p>
</section>
